Dialogue: 10,0:00:07.73,0:00:09.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Kaya is still 19.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:09.98,0:00:10.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I know.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:10.76,0:00:11.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:11.90,0:00:13.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you apologizing?
Dialogue: 10,0:00:13.57,0:00:14.57,Default,,0,0,0,,You're always saying,
Dialogue: 10,0:00:14.57,0:00:17.45,Default,,0,0,0,,"No one will ever take an abrasive woman like you as a bride."
Dialogue: 10,0:00:17.45,0:00:20.58,Default,,0,0,0,,"If a guy like that exists,\N I'd like to meet him."
Dialogue: 10,0:00:20.58,0:00:23.25,Default,,0,0,0,,You should be glad! This is him!
Dialogue: 10,0:00:23.25,0:00:25.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Just look at him! He's \Npretty handsome, right?
Dialogue: 10,0:00:26.71,0:00:28.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:28.04,0:00:29.88,Default,,0,0,0,,He wants to be a mangaka, huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:00:29.88,0:00:31.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:31.09,0:00:33.26,Default,,0,0,0,,He already is one! He's\N been serialized before!
Dialogue: 10,0:00:33.26,0:00:35.72,Default,,0,0,0,,And he's got a new\N one starting in February.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:35.72,0:00:38.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Your friend was a \Nmangaka, wasn't he?
Dialogue: 10,0:00:38.56,0:00:40.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't bring that up now.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:40.43,0:00:43.52,Default,,0,0,0,,He literally put his life \Non the line to draw manga,
Dialogue: 10,0:00:43.52,0:00:44.81,Default,,0,0,0,,and ended up dying because of it.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:44.81,0:00:46.06,Default,,0,0,0,,He died?
Dialogue: 10,0:00:46.06,0:00:48.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Was that friend of yours Kawaguchi Tarou, by any chance?
Dialogue: 10,0:00:50.53,0:00:51.57,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:52.53,0:00:54.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Mashiro Nobuhiro.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:54.07,0:00:56.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,600)}His pen name was Kawaguchi Tarou.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:56.23,0:00:57.95,Default,,0,0,0,,He was
Dialogue: 10,0:00:57.95,0:00:59.45,Default,,0,0,0,,my best friend.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:30.68,0:02:31.96,Default-Italic,,0,0,0,[unreadable!],Shuujin's probably being\N told something like
Dialogue: 10,0:02:32.42,0:02:37.09,Default-Italic,,0,0,0,,"I won't hand my daughter over to a mangaka with such an unstable future!" by now.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:39.80,0:02:40.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:40.72,0:02:42.97,Default,,0,0,0,,So you're working \Nwith his nephew.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:42.97,0:02:44.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-Yes.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:44.35,0:02:46.47,Default,,0,0,0,,It's like fate, isn't it?
Dialogue: 10,0:02:47.81,0:02:50.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you call this \NMashiro Moritaka here?
Dialogue: 10,0:02:51.44,0:02:52.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 10,0:02:52.81,0:02:54.44,Default,,0,0,0,,If they're a team,
Dialogue: 10,0:02:54.44,0:02:57.49,Default,,0,0,0,,then I want to test the team's determination, not just Akito's.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:58.90,0:03:00.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Test their determination?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:04.95,0:03:06.58,Default-Italic,,0,0,0,,Shuujin!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:06.58,0:03:08.37,Default-Italic,,0,0,0,,Did it not work out after all?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:09.37,0:03:10.00,Default,,0,0,0,,What's up?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:10.00,0:03:11.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Saiko!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:11.04,0:03:13.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Team up with me for a karate match against Miyoshi's dad!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:13.29,0:03:14.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:14.32,0:03:15.75,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you on about?!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:15.75,0:03:18.26,Default,,0,0,0,,He wants to test our \Ndetermination as a team!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:18.26,0:03:19.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Please!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:19.01,0:03:20.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I've got nothing to do with this!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:20.72,0:03:23.22,Default,,0,0,0,,But you do!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:23.22,0:03:27.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Apparently, Miyoshi's dad and Kawaguchi Tarou were old friends!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:28.60,0:03:31.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Once that came to light, it seemed like things were looking up,
Dialogue: 10,0:03:31.19,0:03:33.69,Default,,0,0,0,,but then he said he wanted \Nto test our determination.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:37.15,0:03:38.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:38.33,0:03:39.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be right there.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:39.65,0:03:40.78,Default,,0,0,0,,There he is.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:40.78,0:03:41.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Mashiro!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:43.61,0:03:46.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry to call you out \Nwhile you were working.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:46.24,0:03:47.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, Saiko.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:48.58,0:03:49.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Nice to meet you.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:49.58,0:03:51.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Mashiro Moritaka.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:51.50,0:03:53.04,Default,,0,0,0,,You've grown.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:53.92,0:03:55.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I saw you briefly at the funeral.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:56.59,0:03:58.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, let's get to the dojo.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:59.55,0:04:01.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I'll try my best.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:01.63,0:04:02.84,Default,,0,0,0,,R-Right.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:03.63,0:04:05.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Hang in there, Akito...
Dialogue: 10,0:04:12.56,0:04:13.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Please take your time.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:14.81,0:04:16.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Um...
Dialogue: 10,0:04:16.11,0:04:19.40,Default,,0,0,0,,That karate match thing was just an excuse to get you two away.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:19.40,0:04:20.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:20.49,0:04:23.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Some things are difficult to say in front of my wife and daughter.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:24.95,0:04:26.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Mashiro Nobuhiro.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:27.16,0:04:29.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Nobu was my best friend...
Dialogue: 10,0:04:29.18,0:04:31.37,Default,,0,0,0,,and my rival in love.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:32.33,0:04:33.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Rival in love?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:33.75,0:04:35.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Was it Haruno Miyuki?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:36.67,0:04:38.29,Default,,0,0,0,,How do you know about her?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:38.71,0:04:42.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Some letters from her were\N left in my uncle's office.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:42.26,0:04:44.51,Default,,0,0,0,,We got a general idea from those.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:44.51,0:04:45.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:45.66,0:04:47.14,Default,,0,0,0,,The letters, huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:50.26,0:04:53.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Nobu, why'd you\N bring me out here?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:53.06,0:04:55.19,Default,,0,0,0,,You gonna confess your \Nlove to me, or something?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:55.19,0:04:56.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Yosshi...
Dialogue: 10,0:04:56.02,0:04:57.44,Default,,0,0,0,,What, seriously?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:57.44,0:04:59.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll say this only to you.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:59.11,0:05:00.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait! Don't be too hasty!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:00.61,0:05:01.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't swing that way—
Dialogue: 10,0:05:01.03,0:05:02.86,Default-Alt2,,0,0,0,,I just got a letter from Haruno.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:02.86,0:05:04.78,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:04.78,0:05:06.78,Default,,0,0,0,,But this isn't a love letter.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:06.78,0:05:08.91,Default,,0,0,0,,"Let's do our best in high school.",
Dialogue: 10,0:05:08.91,0:05:10.24,Default,,0,0,0,,just that.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:11.74,0:05:13.04,Default,,0,0,0,,She's just shy!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:13.04,0:05:15.79,Default,,0,0,0,,A girl as shy as her sending\N you a letter is pretty much
Dialogue: 10,0:05:15.79,0:05:17.25,Default,,0,0,0,,the confession of a lifetime!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:18.96,0:05:20.50,Default,,0,0,0,,R-Really?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:20.50,0:05:21.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Definitely!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:23.09,0:05:25.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm super jealous,
Dialogue: 10,0:05:25.34,0:05:26.93,Default,,0,0,0,,but I'll be fine, since it's you.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:26.93,0:05:29.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Then can I write a reply?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:29.93,0:05:31.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, go for it!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:32.93,0:05:35.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,950)}I know the rest from\N reading the letters.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:35.73,0:05:37.04,Default,,0,0,0,,In the end,
Dialogue: 10,0:05:37.04,0:05:39.07,Default,,0,0,0,,they never told each\N other their feelings,
Dialogue: 10,0:05:39.07,0:05:41.11,Default,,0,0,0,,and Miyuki married someone else.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:41.11,0:05:42.78,Default,,0,0,0,,He was an idiot.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:42.78,0:05:46.36,Default,,0,0,0,,If he had just told her back then, who knows how things could've turned out?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:46.36,0:05:47.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Um...
Dialogue: 10,0:05:47.32,0:05:47.99,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:48.45,0:05:52.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Miyuki's daughter went\N to our middle school,
Dialogue: 10,0:05:52.62,0:05:55.00,Default,,0,0,0,,and she's dating \NMashiro right now!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:56.16,0:05:57.47,Default,,0,0,0,,And this girl...
Dialogue: 10,0:05:57.47,0:05:59.75,Default,,0,0,0,,well, her name's Azuki Miho.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:59.75,0:06:02.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,590)}She's Kaya's best friend.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:02.50,0:06:04.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Miho?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:04.38,0:06:06.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I hear Kaya talking about\N her sometimes, but I didn't...
Dialogue: 10,0:06:06.76,0:06:08.26,Default,,0,0,0,,About that!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:08.26,0:06:11.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Her dream's been to become a voice actress ever since middle school.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:11.97,0:06:13.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Will Akito be okay?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:14.35,0:06:15.53,Default,,0,0,0,,If he gets a fracture,
Dialogue: 10,0:06:15.53,0:06:17.60,Default,,0,0,0,,he won't be able to \Nwrite manga anymore.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:17.60,0:06:18.94,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't need to worry.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:18.94,0:06:19.52,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 10,0:06:19.52,0:06:22.32,Default,,0,0,0,,The karate thing was just an excuse.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:24.98,0:06:27.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Succeed as a mangaka,
Dialogue: 10,0:06:27.20,0:06:29.41,Default,,0,0,0,,then get married, huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:32.20,0:06:34.04,Default,,0,0,0,,You've done enough, haven't you?!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:34.04,0:06:35.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Why won't you tell her your feelings?!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:35.33,0:06:38.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I was just a bit lucky with \Nmy current serialization!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:38.33,0:06:41.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Until I succeed as a mangaka \Nand can make a living...
Dialogue: 10,0:06:41.13,0:06:44.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you have to do all this\N just to tell her how you feel?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:44.25,0:06:45.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:45.18,0:06:46.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Because I want to marry her!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:46.71,0:06:47.87,Default,,0,0,0,,If I date her,
Dialogue: 10,0:06:47.87,0:06:49.84,Default,,0,0,0,,then it'll be with the\N intention of marriage.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:53.47,0:06:56.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't believe the nephew would take after his uncle so much.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:57.39,0:07:00.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't help but cheer you on too.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:00.60,0:07:02.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Cheer me on...
Dialogue: 10,0:07:02.15,0:07:02.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Then...
Dialogue: 10,0:07:02.94,0:07:04.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:04.09,0:07:05.82,Default,,0,0,0,,After what happened with Nobu,
Dialogue: 10,0:07:05.82,0:07:08.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I think it's best to be with the person you love as soon as possible.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:09.65,0:07:13.37,Default,,0,0,0,,If people make an honest\N effort, it'll work out.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:13.37,0:07:15.53,Default,,0,0,0,,You seem like an honest guy.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:17.12,0:07:18.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you so very much!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:19.08,0:07:20.46,Default,,0,0,0,,You too.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:20.46,0:07:22.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Make your dream come true.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:22.03,0:07:23.88,Default,,0,0,0,,For Nobu's sake as well!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:26.38,0:07:27.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:27.42,0:07:28.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll work hard for it!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:33.22,0:07:36.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm so glad her parents\N were nice people.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:36.43,0:07:39.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I enjoyed learning \Nmore about my uncle.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:40.85,0:07:42.06,Default,,0,0,0,,It's from Azuki.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:42.06,0:07:44.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Instead of replying \Nto me, she calls you?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:44.44,0:07:46.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Congratulations, Takagi!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:46.15,0:07:47.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:47.48,0:07:50.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll do my best so that you and Saiko can get married soon too!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:51.45,0:07:55.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Make sure to always get \Nalong with Kaya and Mashiro!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:55.78,0:07:57.70,Default,,0,0,0,,And with you too.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:57.70,0:07:59.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, thanks!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:59.62,0:08:01.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I have to call Kaya.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:01.25,0:08:02.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm really happy for you two!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:03.50,0:08:04.56,Default,,0,0,0,,All right!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:04.56,0:08:05.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go for it!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:05.88,0:08:07.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's make {\i1}Tanto{\i0} a big hit!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:07.42,0:08:08.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:08.00,0:08:10.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Because your lifestyle depends on it!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:10.88,0:08:11.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't say that!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:11.80,0:08:13.38,Default,,0,0,0,,The pressure's gonna kill me!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:13.38,0:08:14.34,Default,,0,0,0,,My bad!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:17.43,0:08:19.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Here, please take this ticket.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:19.81,0:08:21.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Th-Thanks.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:21.06,0:08:22.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, you're here.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:22.44,0:08:23.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Miura.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:23.02,0:08:25.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, but I'm still \Ngetting things ready.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:25.69,0:08:26.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Go on without me.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:26.98,0:08:27.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:28.44,0:08:29.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Um...
Dialogue: 10,0:08:29.44,0:08:30.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Ashirogi!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:31.19,0:08:32.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Fukuda!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:32.57,0:08:33.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Aoki too!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:33.53,0:08:34.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Good evening.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:34.66,0:08:36.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I came too.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:36.24,0:08:37.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:37.49,0:08:40.95,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no way you'd miss the New Year's party, Hiramaru.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:40.95,0:08:41.87,Default,,0,0,0,,That's true.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:42.46,0:08:43.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Hattori!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:43.71,0:08:45.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, congrats on \Nyour new serialization!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:45.50,0:08:48.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, enjoy the party.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:48.13,0:08:48.96,Default,,0,0,0,,O-Okay...
Dialogue: 10,0:08:48.96,0:08:52.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Ibaraki, editor-in-chief of {\i1}Jack SQ{\i0}.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:52.97,0:08:56.14,Default,,0,0,0,,We're aware of \N{\i1}+NATURAL{\i0}'s reputation.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:56.14,0:08:56.89,Default,,0,0,0,,By the way,
Dialogue: 10,0:08:56.89,0:08:59.14,Default,,0,0,0,,if there are any other stories you'd like to write, by all means—
Dialogue: 10,0:08:58.22,0:08:59.47,Default-Alt,,0,0,0,,Akina!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:59.47,0:09:00.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Hattori!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:00.81,0:09:02.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I read your fax.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:02.64,0:09:04.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Chapter seven was well done.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:04.48,0:09:05.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:05.73,0:09:08.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you have any \Nquestions or concerns?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:08.69,0:09:09.57,Default,,0,0,0,,If you do, I'll quickly—
Dialogue: 10,0:09:09.57,0:09:10.23,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:10.23,0:09:11.94,Default,,0,0,0,,None at all. It was fantastic.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:11.94,0:09:14.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Enjoy yourself today.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:14.03,0:09:16.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, the seventh \Nchapter was good too?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:16.66,0:09:17.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:17.36,0:09:20.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm so excited to read \Nwhat happens next!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:22.16,0:09:25.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Hattori, I want to read the \Nseventh chapter right away.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:25.37,0:09:26.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:26.20,0:09:27.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Right after the party.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:27.42,0:09:28.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm looking forward to it!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:28.63,0:09:30.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know much about it,
Dialogue: 10,0:09:30.64,0:09:33.30,Default,,0,0,0,,but there's some pretty\N good hype for {\i1}Natural{\i0}.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:33.30,0:09:34.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:34.76,0:09:36.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you think they're being kind of cold?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:37.30,0:09:39.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I was really surprised though!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:39.55,0:09:43.18,Default,,0,0,0,,You've shown some real talent by taking Akina Aiko's manuscript this far!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:43.18,0:09:44.10,Default,,0,0,0,,That's true,
Dialogue: 10,0:09:44.10,0:09:46.31,Default,,0,0,0,,but you're something else too.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:46.31,0:09:49.98,Default,,0,0,0,,You thought of having \NNiizuma draw another manga.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:49.98,0:09:50.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes,
Dialogue: 10,0:09:50.80,0:09:54.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm happy to have a popular author in {\i1}Jack{\i0} draw it for me.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:54.07,0:09:57.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Indeed, Hattori is the rising star of the editorial department.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:57.49,0:09:58.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, please.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:58.91,0:10:00.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:00.16,0:10:03.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Hattori is a rising star!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:04.08,0:10:06.04,Default,,0,0,0,,A rising star?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:06.04,0:10:09.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Niizuma, will you really be \Nokay with five assistants?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:09.79,0:10:11.46,Default,,0,0,0,,No problem!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:11.46,0:10:14.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be {\i1}Jack'{\i0}s number \None author this year too!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:14.76,0:10:16.52,Default,,0,0,0,,It seems like the editorial department's
Dialogue: 10,0:10:16.52,0:10:18.30,Default,,0,0,0,,expecting a lot more from \N{\i1}Natural{\i0} than {\i1}Tanto{\i0}!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:18.30,0:10:20.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's prove them wrong shall we?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:20.30,0:10:22.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I definitely don't \Nwant to lose to Iwase.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:22.35,0:10:23.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:23.26,0:10:24.97,Default,,0,0,0,,This time we'll overtake Eiji!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:24.97,0:10:27.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for coming today.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:27.94,0:10:29.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Arai, what are you doing after this?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:29.48,0:10:31.94,Default,,0,0,0,,There are things we can't talk about while the editors are around.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:31.94,0:10:33.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Then let's go somewhere else.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:33.90,0:10:35.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Fukuda!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:35.94,0:10:38.36,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you talking\N about with Aoki?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:38.36,0:10:40.11,Default,,0,0,0,,That's unfair!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:40.11,0:10:41.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's all go to the afterparty!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:41.82,0:10:45.70,Default,,0,0,0,,But Ashirogi and Master \NNiizuma are still underage.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:45.70,0:10:46.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Akina too.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:46.83,0:10:49.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Then we can just go \Nto a family restaurant!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:49.33,0:10:51.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll get Niizuma-sensei.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:51.00,0:10:52.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Niizuma-sensei, let's go to a—
Dialogue: 10,0:10:52.96,0:10:56.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I need to get back to \Nwork, so I'm going home.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:56.67,0:10:57.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Work?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:57.42,0:11:01.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to make a name \Nfor the seventh chapter.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:01.43,0:11:03.47,Default,,0,0,0,,You've already done up\N through to the third chapter,
Dialogue: 10,0:11:03.47,0:11:05.56,Default,,0,0,0,,there's no need to rush.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:05.56,0:11:06.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Right, right!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:06.89,0:11:08.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Forget about work for today!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:08.89,0:11:10.48,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I won't!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:10.90,0:11:13.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm having fun drawing\N manga right now!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:13.40,0:11:16.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I could barely pull myself away from drawing to come here today!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:16.03,0:11:19.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, I'll go grab it from\N the editorial department.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:19.82,0:11:22.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, SEE YOU AGAIN!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:22.03,0:11:24.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmph, party-pooper.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:24.62,0:11:26.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Then how about the rest of us go—
Dialogue: 10,0:11:27.37,0:11:28.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:28.75,0:11:30.00,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:30.00,0:11:30.86,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:30.86,0:11:32.58,Default,,0,0,0,,They've all gone home.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:33.33,0:11:35.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Hiramaru, what are you \Ndoing there all alone?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:36.80,0:11:37.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Yoshida-shi...
Dialogue: 10,0:11:41.47,0:11:43.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Akira, you were too obvious.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:44.30,0:11:45.55,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:45.55,0:11:48.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Giving Ashirogi that \Nmuch incentive...
Dialogue: 10,0:11:48.81,0:11:50.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you backing\N them so much?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:53.15,0:11:54.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Niizuma,
Dialogue: 10,0:11:54.46,0:11:58.82,Default,,0,0,0,,it isn't good practice to support authors one isn't in charge of.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:58.82,0:12:00.24,Default,,0,0,0,,If it looked like that to you,
Dialogue: 10,0:12:00.24,0:12:02.53,Default,,0,0,0,,please don't tell anyone else.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:02.53,0:12:04.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I know.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:04.20,0:12:06.24,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why I'm bringing it up now.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:07.12,0:12:11.37,Default,,0,0,0,,In the future, Ashirogi will become one of the pillars of Jack.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:11.37,0:12:13.17,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what I believe.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:13.17,0:12:15.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Just like you are.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:15.42,0:12:17.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I think so too,
Dialogue: 10,0:12:17.63,0:12:19.42,Default,,0,0,0,,and I want it to happen soon.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:20.05,0:12:23.09,Default,,0,0,0,,So no matter how you \Nsupport them, I'll help you!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:23.51,0:12:24.05,Default,,0,0,0,,However...
Dialogue: 10,0:12:25.34,0:12:26.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't lose to them!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:36.40,0:12:37.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Nice to meet you!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:37.53,0:12:38.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Orihara Ichiriki!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:38.94,0:12:40.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Looking forward to working together!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:40.32,0:12:43.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Orihara got an honorable \Nmention for the Tezuka Prize.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:43.61,0:12:47.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I've got Takahama too, so \Nyou guys should be all set.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:47.49,0:12:49.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm the artist, Mashiro.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:49.33,0:12:50.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm the writer, Takagi.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:50.58,0:12:52.91,Default,,0,0,0,,And I'm his wife, Takagi Kaya!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:52.91,0:12:53.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Nice to meet you!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:54.00,0:12:55.16,Default,,0,0,0,,H-Huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:55.16,0:12:56.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Wife?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:56.25,0:12:58.42,Default,,0,0,0,,They registered at \Nthe end of last year.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:59.30,0:13:01.55,Default,,0,0,0,,You're a freshman in college with a serialization {\i1}and{\i0} a wife?!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:01.55,0:13:02.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Awesome!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:02.57,0:13:03.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Too awesome!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:03.76,0:13:06.97,Default,,0,0,0,,There really {\i1}are{\i0} a ton\N of strange mangakas!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:07.59,0:13:09.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll do my best too!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:12.10,0:13:15.48,Default,,0,0,0,,The two of us will live\N here from now on.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:17.35,0:13:19.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm so happy!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:19.61,0:13:22.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Your dad's giving us the\N realtor hookup, huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:25.40,0:13:26.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's be happy.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:27.49,0:13:28.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:29.03,0:13:31.29,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I'll {\i1}make{\i0} us happy.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:48.43,0:13:49.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:49.14,0:13:50.75,Default,,0,0,0,,All right!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:50.75,0:13:53.02,Default,,0,0,0,,The first chapter's done!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:53.02,0:13:54.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Good work, everybody.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:55.27,0:13:57.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I brought the publishing\N sample of {\i1}+NATURAL.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:58.27,0:13:59.79,Default,,0,0,0,,An opening color page?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:59.79,0:14:01.48,Default,,0,0,0,,And {\i1}Crow{\i0}'s got one in the middle?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:01.48,0:14:03.28,Default,,0,0,0,,It's already a Niiuzma Eiji issue.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:03.78,0:14:06.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, he's drawing both of them.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:06.20,0:14:08.86,Default,,0,0,0,,They don't want people \Nto overlook either of them.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:08.86,0:14:10.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway, let's check out {\i1}Natural{\i0}.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:10.20,0:14:10.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:14.75,0:14:16.41,Default,,0,0,0,,This is good!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:16.41,0:14:18.29,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not just good!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:18.71,0:14:21.04,Default,,0,0,0,,It's got an indie vibe.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:21.04,0:14:24.03,Default,,0,0,0,,And even though all the conventions of a first chapter are being broken,
Dialogue: 10,0:14:24.03,0:14:26.01,Default,,0,0,0,,it still feels mainstream!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:26.47,0:14:28.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Indie? Mainstream?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:28.17,0:14:29.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't get it.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:29.39,0:14:32.18,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not about defeating some enemy
Dialogue: 10,0:14:32.18,0:14:34.32,Default,,0,0,0,,and wrapping things \Nup in one chapter,
Dialogue: 10,0:14:34.32,0:14:36.27,Default,,0,0,0,,but you can definitely \Ntell it's a shounen manga.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:36.85,0:14:38.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:38.19,0:14:40.08,Default,,0,0,0,,He's following the pattern\N of stuff like Pokémon
Dialogue: 10,0:14:40.08,0:14:41.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,390)}by hatching the egg into various monsters.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:41.77,0:14:44.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, {\i1}that{\i0} I can understand.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:44.33,0:14:45.69,Default,,0,0,0,,That's super mainstream!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:45.69,0:14:46.94,Default,,0,0,0,,As for franchise opportunities,
Dialogue: 10,0:14:46.94,0:14:49.99,Default,,0,0,0,,if it were turned into a card game, kids would probably love it.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:50.78,0:14:52.32,Default,,0,0,0,,And an anime too.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:53.66,0:14:55.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Speaking of anime adaptations...
Dialogue: 10,0:14:55.37,0:14:58.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Otters 11{\i0} will be turned \Ninto a late-night anime!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:59.37,0:15:00.25,Default,,0,0,0,,No way!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:00.25,0:15:02.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Not even I could lie about that.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:04.04,0:15:05.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Yoshida-shi!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:05.84,0:15:07.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm so glad I listened to you!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:07.38,0:15:09.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been a terrible\N person for thinking of you
Dialogue: 10,0:15:09.93,0:15:12.47,Default,,0,0,0,,as a long-haired narcissistic con man who tricks me time and time again!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:12.47,0:15:15.10,Default,,0,0,0,,So that's how you think of me?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:15.10,0:15:17.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, not that you're wrong.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:17.31,0:15:19.10,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll announce it in \Nthe magazine this spring.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:19.10,0:15:20.60,Default,,0,0,0,,The anime starts in the fall.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:20.60,0:15:22.86,Default,,0,0,0,,You understand, \Ndon't you, Hiramaru?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:22.86,0:15:23.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:23.86,0:15:24.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Until fall...
Dialogue: 10,0:15:24.78,0:15:28.65,Default,,0,0,0,,No, for the rest of the year, I won't breathe a word about taking a break!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:29.74,0:15:31.16,Default,,0,0,0,,By the way,
Dialogue: 10,0:15:31.16,0:15:33.03,Default,,0,0,0,,why a late-night slot?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:34.37,0:15:38.83,Default-Italic,,0,0,0,,I can't tell him that no\N matter how long we wait,
Dialogue: 10,0:15:38.83,0:15:41.08,Default-Italic,,0,0,0,,we'll never get an offer \Nfor an evening timeslot.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:41.08,0:15:41.58,Default-Italic,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:42.00,0:15:45.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, you know, it has\N a pretty dark theme.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:45.04,0:15:46.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I see!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:47.00,0:15:49.34,Default-Italic,,0,0,0,,This should be good for a while.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:50.01,0:15:51.84,Default-Italic,,0,0,0,,Oh I'm just too much!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:52.26,0:15:54.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Otters{\i0} and {\i1}Crow{\i0} got an anime.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:54.43,0:15:56.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Fukuda and Aoki's look promising,
Dialogue: 10,0:15:56.78,0:15:59.68,Default,,0,0,0,,so if we don't pull out all the\N stops, we'll be left behind.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:00.89,0:16:03.10,Default,,0,0,0,,The first chapter of {\i1}Tanto{\i0} has already been sent to the press.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:03.10,0:16:05.65,Default,,0,0,0,,The names up to chapter \Nthree have been finalized.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:05.65,0:16:07.90,Default,,0,0,0,,The rest is out of our hands.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:08.44,0:16:11.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, have you come up with\N an idea for the invention
Dialogue: 10,0:16:11.68,0:16:13.24,Default,,0,0,0,,that'll appear in the fourth chapter?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:13.24,0:16:14.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Not yet...
Dialogue: 10,0:16:14.82,0:16:18.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I was going to wait for the results of the first chapter and revise it based on that.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:18.24,0:16:19.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Still,
Dialogue: 10,0:16:19.34,0:16:21.83,Default,,0,0,0,,you need to be brainstorming\N ideas one after another.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:21.83,0:16:23.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Otherwise, you can't move forward.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:23.71,0:16:25.04,Default,,0,0,0,,You're right.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:25.79,0:16:28.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll make a list by tomorrow.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:31.84,0:16:33.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:33.05,0:16:34.30,Default,,0,0,0,,That'll be 250 yen.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:34.30,0:16:36.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:36.43,0:16:37.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you need a bag?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:37.68,0:16:38.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:38.14,0:16:39.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay then.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:39.26,0:16:40.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Here's your change: 10 yen.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:40.64,0:16:42.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you. Please come again.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:43.27,0:16:44.73,Default,,0,0,0,,This is crazy!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:44.73,0:16:45.84,Default,,0,0,0,,This week's Jack
Dialogue: 10,0:16:45.84,0:16:48.36,Default,,0,0,0,,is completely sold out in every \Nconvenience store and bookstore!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:48.36,0:16:49.98,Default,,0,0,0,,It's only 3 PM on a Monday!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:50.48,0:16:52.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it the Niizuma Eiji effect?!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:52.36,0:16:52.91,Default,,0,0,0,,No way.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:52.91,0:16:53.86,Default,,0,0,0,,It has to be a coincidence!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:53.86,0:16:55.82,Default,,0,0,0,,No, you're exactly right.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:55.82,0:16:58.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone was buzzing about it on the Internet yesterday before it went on sale.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:58.62,0:17:03.00,Default,,0,0,0,,They were saying that\N{\i1} +NATURAL{\i0} is going to be great!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:05.54,0:17:07.08,Default,,0,0,0,,My apologies.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:07.08,0:17:08.59,Default,,0,0,0,,All copies were sold out yesterday.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:10.63,0:17:12.26,Default,,0,0,0,,It's first place in \Nthe preliminary polls!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:12.26,0:17:13.01,Default,,0,0,0,,We did it!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:18.97,0:17:20.93,Default,,0,0,0,,And now for the final results...
Dialogue: 10,0:17:20.93,0:17:22.89,Default,,0,0,0,,It's first place by a long shot!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:22.89,0:17:24.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Crow{\i0}'s in fourth.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:24.69,0:17:26.60,Default,,0,0,0,,All that's changed since \Nit ranked third last week
Dialogue: 10,0:17:26.60,0:17:28.11,Default,,0,0,0,,is{\i1} Natural{\i0} being placed at the top.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:28.56,0:17:29.94,Default,,0,0,0,,It's perfect.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:31.07,0:17:33.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Natural{\i0} is first place, after all?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:33.53,0:17:34.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I really don't want {\i1}Tanto{\i0}'s
Dialogue: 10,0:17:34.80,0:17:37.36,Default,,0,0,0,,first chapter to rank under\N{\i1} Natural {\i0}'s second chapter.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:37.36,0:17:39.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I know how you feel,
Dialogue: 10,0:17:39.36,0:17:42.12,Default,,0,0,0,,but plot-driven manga and \Ngag manga are different.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:42.12,0:17:44.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Anything in the top \Nthree is a great success.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:44.01,0:17:45.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Even top five is great.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:45.12,0:17:46.83,Default,,0,0,0,,That doesn't matter.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:47.54,0:17:49.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Natural{\i0} was first place.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:49.33,0:17:50.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Tanto{\i0} will be first too!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:50.54,0:17:51.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:55.80,0:17:57.47,Default,,0,0,0,,We stopped by the \Nconvenience store, but...
Dialogue: 10,0:17:58.55,0:18:00.93,Default,,0,0,0,,...there were a lot left this week.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:01.64,0:18:03.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry about that!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:03.80,0:18:05.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Last week was unusual!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:05.53,0:18:07.44,Default,,0,0,0,,By this time tomorrow...
Dialogue: 10,0:18:07.44,0:18:10.40,Default,,0,0,0,,No, by {\i1}tonight{\i0}, they'll all be gone!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:19.66,0:18:20.74,Default,,0,0,0,,It's Miura!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:20.74,0:18:21.49,Default,,0,0,0,,It must be the results!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:23.83,0:18:25.62,Default,,0,0,0,,You got fifth place!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:26.66,0:18:27.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Fifth...
Dialogue: 10,0:18:29.29,0:18:30.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:30.91,0:18:32.21,Default,,0,0,0,,What's with that reaction?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:32.21,0:18:33.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I told you before that
Dialogue: 10,0:18:33.25,0:18:35.26,Default,,0,0,0,,getting fifth place with a \Ngag manga is a {\i1}good{\i0} thing!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:35.26,0:18:37.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah...
Dialogue: 10,0:18:37.22,0:18:38.72,Default,,0,0,0,,What about {\i1}Natural{\i0}?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:40.72,0:18:42.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Third?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:42.18,0:18:43.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes...
Dialogue: 10,0:18:43.45,0:18:44.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes...
Dialogue: 10,0:18:45.47,0:18:46.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Crow{\i0} was fourth.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:48.60,0:18:51.10,Default-Italic,,0,0,0,,I read {\i0}Hirameki! Tanto-kun.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:51.10,0:18:55.11,Default-Italic,,0,0,0,,It'll definitely be a \Nbig hit with the kids!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:56.03,0:18:57.48,Default-Italic,,0,0,0,,Kids...
Dialogue: 10,0:18:57.48,0:18:58.49,Default-Italic,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:10.75,0:19:13.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, cheer up already.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:13.71,0:19:17.55,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll feel a lot better if \Nyou move around some!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:18.26,0:19:18.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:18.76,0:19:20.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Was there more stuff coming?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:20.88,0:19:22.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Coming!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:24.85,0:19:25.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Iwase!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:26.56,0:19:28.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Congratulations on your marriage.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:28.39,0:19:31.27,Default,,0,0,0,,How do you know where we live?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:31.27,0:19:34.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I called your parent's house.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:36.44,0:19:39.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I really just wanted \Nto congratulate you.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:39.70,0:19:41.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:42.32,0:19:42.78,Default,,0,0,0,,See ya.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:43.28,0:19:43.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait a minute!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:43.99,0:19:46.12,Default,,0,0,0,,"Just wanted to congratulate us?!"
Dialogue: 10,0:19:46.12,0:19:49.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Until a little while ago, you were saying you were in love with my man!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:49.08,0:19:50.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I read that letter!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:50.71,0:19:52.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop it!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:52.04,0:19:55.13,Default,,0,0,0,,But I can't take her \Ncongratulations seriously!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:55.13,0:19:58.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I liked the Takagi with talent.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:02.13,0:20:04.47,Default,,0,0,0,,What the hell does that mean?!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:03.26,0:20:04.47,Default-Alt2,,0,0,0,,Stop, I said!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:05.10,0:20:07.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Natural{\i0} was more popular!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:07.06,0:20:08.72,Default,,0,0,0,,You have more talent than me!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:08.72,0:20:10.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Without a doubt!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:10.27,0:20:12.31,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what you wanted\N to hear, right, Iwase?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:12.31,0:20:13.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:16.31,0:20:18.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Take this back.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:19.19,0:20:20.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Ever since middle school,
Dialogue: 10,0:20:20.72,0:20:23.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Takagi Akito has only\N had eyes for me.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:23.70,0:20:26.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't need your congratulations.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:26.87,0:20:31.33,Default,,0,0,0,,You should hurry up and find some other guy with more talent than him.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:31.33,0:20:32.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I already have.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:32.25,0:20:33.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:33.55,0:20:34.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Who is it?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:34.58,0:20:35.54,Default,,0,0,0,,You're just blowing hot air.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:40.26,0:20:41.88,Default,,0,0,0,,It's Hattori!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:42.51,0:20:43.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Your editor?!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:43.63,0:20:44.30,Default,,0,0,0,,He's your boyfriend?!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:44.30,0:20:45.68,Default,,0,0,0,,No...
Dialogue: 10,0:20:45.68,0:20:48.81,Default,,0,0,0,,But he's a man with great \Ntalent that I can admire.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:49.31,0:20:51.27,Default,,0,0,0,,He's the man I like.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:58.90,0:21:00.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Your sixth chapter \Ncame in 11th, as well.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:00.98,0:21:02.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Same as last week.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:02.65,0:21:04.24,Default,,0,0,0,,The first chapter was 5th,
Dialogue: 10,0:21:04.24,0:21:05.74,Default,,0,0,0,,the second was 9th,
Dialogue: 10,0:21:05.74,0:21:07.07,Default,,0,0,0,,the third was 10th,
Dialogue: 10,0:21:07.07,0:21:08.87,Default,,0,0,0,,and ever since then, \Nit's stayed at 11th place.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:09.28,0:21:11.29,Default,,0,0,0,,In a sense, it's stable.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:11.29,0:21:14.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, guys, you should feel proud.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:14.12,0:21:16.71,Default,,0,0,0,,The lead editor even \Nsaid it's been a long time
Dialogue: 10,0:21:16.71,0:21:19.29,Default,,0,0,0,,since Jack had a manga that's well-received by the younger readers.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:20.05,0:21:21.17,Default,,0,0,0,,He did?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:21.17,0:21:21.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:22.17,0:21:24.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Kids usually pick \Ntheir top three manga
Dialogue: 10,0:21:24.01,0:21:28.01,Default,,0,0,0,,based on how funny they think it is, not the quality of the plot.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:28.01,0:21:30.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Gag manga have the advantage there.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:31.35,0:21:32.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't care about that!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:32.93,0:21:36.52,Default,,0,0,0,,We have to think about\N how we can do better!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:37.31,0:21:38.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Better, huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:39.61,0:21:41.78,Default,,0,0,0,,How to pull in more kids?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:41.78,0:21:45.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Will {\i1}Tanto{\i0} become a boom, \Nor will {\i1}Tanto{\i0} start a boom?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:45.99,0:21:48.41,Default,,0,0,0,,A boom, a boom...
Dialogue: 10,0:21:48.41,0:21:49.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Starting a boom with a gag manga...
Dialogue: 10,0:21:49.62,0:21:52.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Some signature joke that \Nwill stick in kids' heads...
Dialogue: 10,0:21:52.37,0:21:53.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, that's it!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:53.58,0:21:57.50,Default,,0,0,0,,It may be a bit old, but \Nsomething like Iyami's "Shii!"
Dialogue: 10,0:21:57.50,0:22:00.09,Default,,0,0,0,,If you repeat the same joke over and over, it'll start a fad!
Dialogue: 10,0:22:00.54,0:22:01.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I can try for it,
Dialogue: 10,0:22:01.76,0:22:03.96,Default,,0,0,0,,but I don't know if I can do it.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:03.96,0:22:05.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll work at it.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:05.38,0:22:07.05,Default,,0,0,0,,If I have something repeatable,
Dialogue: 10,0:22:07.05,0:22:09.18,Default,,0,0,0,,it might make writing jokes easier.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:09.18,0:22:10.60,Default-Italic,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:10.60,0:22:13.01,Default-Italic,,0,0,0,,We can get better rankings \Nif we change how we do things!
Dialogue: 10,0:22:14.18,0:22:15.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Good work.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:15.48,0:22:17.42,Default,,0,0,0,,The seventh chapter's \Nstill at 2nd place...
Dialogue: 10,0:22:17.42,0:22:19.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Natural{\i0} is really something.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:19.48,0:22:21.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, it's not like {\i1}Crow{\i0} \Ndropped in popularity.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:21.68,0:22:23.94,Default,,0,0,0,,It actually got more votes.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:24.40,0:22:25.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Speaking of rankings,
Dialogue: 10,0:22:25.68,0:22:30.07,Default,,0,0,0,,your favorite Ashirogi has\N settled at 11th place.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:31.16,0:22:34.70,Default,,0,0,0,,The editorial department is saying things like, "Looks like Ashirogi can do gag manga too,"
Dialogue: 10,0:22:34.70,0:22:37.29,Default,,0,0,0,,and "Manga that bring in \Nyounger readers are valuable."
Dialogue: 10,0:22:37.29,0:22:40.00,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you think of {\i1}Tanto{\i0}?
Dialogue: 10,0:22:40.00,0:22:41.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not reading it
Dialogue: 10,0:22:41.29,0:22:43.75,Default,,0,0,0,,anymore!
Dialogue: 10,0:22:43.75,0:22:44.92,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 10,0:24:15.60,0:24:18.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it okay for us to \Ncontinue {\i1}Tanto{\i0} like this?
Dialogue: 10,0:24:18.06,0:24:20.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't say something so unnerving right before my wedding ceremony!{FUCK YEAH}
Dialogue: 10,0:24:21.02,0:24:22.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Next time on {\i1}Bakuman:
Dialogue: 10,0:24:22.23,0:24:23.65,Default,,0,0,0,,"Love and Denial."
Dialogue: 10,0:24:23.65,0:24:25.02,Default,,0,0,0,,In order to achieve your dream,
Dialogue: 10,0:24:25.02,0:24:26.86,Default,,0,0,0,,you need to stick to your goals!
